welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Laurel! Known for its charming small-town feel and rich history, we hope you'll take the time to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer. Have a wonderful stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport handles all commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Tipton AAF Airport is used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport is the primary hub for all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is home to many major airlines, including American Airlines, Delta, and United.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B serves as the hub for Southwest Airlines and other budget airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may require a password for access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Montgomery County Airport houses the check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Montgomery County Airport serves private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport primarily serves American Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: Terminal B/C
terminals.description: Terminal B/C at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves various airlines, including Delta, JetBlue, and United.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free Wi-Fi throughout the airport by connecting to the DCA Free Wi-Fi network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lee Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Lee Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Potomac Airfield Airport serves all commercial flights and includes various amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Potomac Airfield Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a more exclusive and personalized experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy complimentary wifi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including dining options, souvenir shops, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport caters to private and corporate jets, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for its passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
